OL,3,CLecturer 'can't wait for wedding
OL,4,Ctoast' after tremor treatment
OL,6,FA university lecturer who has spent
OL,7,Fhis whole life with a tremor says he
OL,8,Fis looking forward to raising a toast
OL,9,Fat his wedding after undergoing a
OL,10,Fcutting-edge treatment.
OL,12,FSteve O'Connor, 53, from Manchester,
OL,13,Fhas a neurological condition called
OL,14,FEssential Tremor which causes his
OL,15,Fright hand to shake uncontrollably.
OL,17,F"I can't hold a cup and bring it to my
OL,18,Fmouth without the water spilling out",
OL,19,Fhe explains.
