OL,3,CLecturer 'can't wait for wedding
OL,4,Ctoast' after tremor treatment
OL,6,F"I've had Essential Tremor all my
OL,7,Flife, so I've never known anything
OL,8,Fdifferent. But over lockdown a couple
OL,9,Fof years ago, the tremors got much
OL,10,Fworse.
OL,12,FSteve says the treatment will have a
OL,13,Fprofound impact on his life
OL,15,F"I lecture in Creative Writing, so
OL,16,Fbeing able to write on a whiteboard
OL,17,Fand even hold a pen to write on paper
OL,18,Fis incredibly important to me.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/16
