OL,3,CLecturer 'can't wait for wedding
OL,4,Ctoast' after tremor treatment
OL,6,F"I've had to explain to people and
OL,7,Fdeclare I have a tremor, otherwise
OL,8,Fthey make all sorts of assumptions.
OL,10,F"As a performance poet, people think
OL,11,FI'm nervous when my hand shakes - but
OL,12,FI'm not a nervous person."
OL,14,FBut now thanks to a pioneering
OL,15,Ftreatment at The Walton Centre in
OL,16,FLiverpool, he is tremor free in his
OL,17,Fright hand.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/16
