OL,3,CLecturer 'can't wait for wedding
OL,4,Ctoast' after tremor treatment
OL,6,FIn a UK first, ITV Granada Reports was
OL,7,Finvited to film the procedure, as
OL,8,FSteve became the 100th patient to
OL,9,Freceive Trans-cranial MR-guided
OL,10,FFocused Ultrasound, or Focused
OL,11,FUltrasound for short.
OL,13,FSpeaking ahead of the treatment, Steve
OL,14,Fsaid he was anxious: "I just want the
OL,15,Ftremor gone. I really want it to work.
OL,17,F"It's going to be weird and
OL,18,Frevolutionary to not have it. I've
OL,19,Fnever known that."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/16
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
