OL,3,CLecturer 'can't wait for wedding
OL,4,Ctoast' after tremor treatment
OL,6,FMr Jibril Osman Farah is Consultant
OL,7,FNeurosurgeon and lead clinician for
OL,8,Fthe project and with his team,
OL,9,Fperformed Steve's treatment.
OL,11,FThe incisionless procedure involves
OL,12,Fthermal tissue ablation, targeted at
OL,13,Fthe key areas of the brain causing the
OL,14,Ftremors.
OL,16,FMr Farah said nearly one thousand
OL,17,Fultrasound beams were focused onto a
OL,18,Fspot, around five millimetres in
OL,19,Fdiameter, in Steve's brain.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/16
