OL,6,FBy burning it, he is then able to
OL,7,F'break the circuit' of the tremor and
OL,8,Fstabilise Steve's hand.
OL,10,FConsultant Surgeon Mr Jibril Osman
OL,11,FFarah explains the procedure
OL,13,FSteve is asked to draw spirals and
OL,14,Flines on a piece of paper before,
OL,15,Fduring and after his treatment so the
OL,16,Fteam can monitor his progress - and
OL,17,Fthe difference is remarkable.
