OL,6,FSince the service launch in April
OL,7,F2022, 100 patients have undergone the
OL,8,Fprocedure at The Walton Centre the
OL,9,Fonly hospital trust in the UK
OL,10,Fspecialising in neurology,
OL,11,Fneurosurgery and pain services.
OL,13,FIt is one of only two NHS hospitals in
OL,14,Fthe UK to offer Focused Ultrasound for
OL,15,FEssential Tremor, and the first in the
OL,16,FNorth of England.
OL,18,FEssential Tremor is a neurological
OL,19,Fdisorder that causes an uncontrollable
OL,20,Fshake or trembling in a part of the
OL,21,Fbody.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/16
