OL,4,Ctoast' after tremor treatment
OL,6,FIt is one of the most common
OL,7,Fneurological movement disorders,
OL,8,Faffecting around one million people in
OL,9,Fthe UK and is thought to be eight to
OL,10,F10 times more prevalent than
OL,11,FParkinsons disease, according to the
OL,12,FNational Tremor Foundation.
OL,14,FSpeaking less than 24 hours after his
OL,15,Ftreatment, Steve said: "I feel really
OL,16,Fgood. I have had two cups of tea and
OL,17,Ftwo hot chocolates without spilling
OL,18,Fthem all over myself.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/16
