OL,3,CLecturer 'can't wait for wedding
OL,4,Ctoast' after tremor treatment
OL,6,F"The first response I saw was my
OL,7,Fpartner's - an emotional moment that
OL,8,Freally got me. Having Focused
OL,9,FUltrasound on my dominant side has
OL,10,Fbeen revolutionary.
OL,12,F"It's new to have a hand that doesn't
OL,13,Ftremor, and I can't tell you how much
OL,14,Fit means to me."
OL,16,FCurrently, eligible patients get one
OL,17,FFocused Ultrasound treatment to reduce
OL,18,Fthe tremors on one side of their body.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/16
