OL,6,FCurrent regulatory approvals
OL,7,Fdemonstrate good clinical durability,
OL,8,Fwith tremor relief maintained at three
OL,9,Fyears.
OL,11,FMaureen Greenough from St Helens was
OL,12,Fthe first patient to receive the
OL,13,Ftreatment at the Walton Centre in
OL,14,F2022. She describes it as 'life-
OL,15,Fchanging"
OL,17,FBack at the hospital to celebrate the
OL,18,Fmilestone, she met with Steve and
OL,19,Fsaid: "I couldn't believe how
OL,20,Fimmediate the change was.
