OL,4,Ctoast' after tremor treatment
OL,6,F"As soon as I left the treatment room
OL,7,FI noticed that my right hand had
OL,8,Fstopped shaking, it was like the team
OL,9,Fat The Walton Centre had flipped a
OL,10,Fswitch!
OL,12,F"Before this my writing was terrible,
OL,13,FI couldn't hold a cup without using
OL,14,Fboth hands.
OL,16,F"I felt a lot of embarrassment and I
OL,17,Fdidn't feel comfortable eating in
OL,18,Ffront of people. Now that's all
OL,19,Fchanged.
