OL,4,Ctoast' after tremor treatment
OL,6,F"There's no more embarrassment - I
OL,7,Fused to be frightened to go out with
OL,8,Fpeople, I felt like they were staring
OL,9,Fat my tremor, now there's nothing for
OL,10,Fthem to see.
OL,12,F"The treatment The Walton Centre
OL,13,Fprovides is excellent, and I will be
OL,14,Fforever grateful to the team for
OL,15,Fhelping me."
OL,17,FGranada Reports followed Maureen's
OL,18,Fstory exclusively in 2022.
