OL,6,FMedical Director Dr Andrew Nicolson
OL,7,Fsaid: "The clinical teams have been
OL,8,Ffull steam aheadJsince the service
OL,9,Flaunch in 2022.
OL,11,F"All of those who have been treated
OL,12,Fwith Focused Ultrasound have seen huge
OL,13,Fbenefits, the majority seeing their
OL,14,Ftremors essentially disappear as soon
OL,15,Fas the procedure is over.
OL,17,F"Before, patients would have to
OL,18,Fundergo major surgery to achieve
OL,19,Fsimilar results, so it's certainly a
OL,20,Fmilestone to be proud of."
