OL,6,FSteve explains how life changed
OL,7,Fimmediately after his treatment.
OL,9,FMr Osman Farah said: "We've had a very
OL,10,Fproductive two years delivering this
OL,11,Fservice to patients with Essential
OL,12,FTremor.
OL,14,F"The outcomes have been nothing short
OL,15,Fof incredible. I'm regularly seeing
OL,16,Fpatients returning to clinic after
OL,17,Ftreatment continuing to be tremor-free.
