OL,6,F"It's an ongoing team effort, and I'm
OL,7,Fdelighted we can continue to offer
OL,8,Fthis pioneering treatment to patients,
OL,9,Fand expand it in the future."
OL,11,FLong term plans for the ongoing
OL,12,Fdelivery of the procedure include
OL,13,Freviewing patients who have had the
OL,14,Ftreatment for a second round, to
OL,15,Faddress their other side of their body.
OL,17,FSteve is now getting on with planning
OL,18,Fhis future without the tremor in his
OL,19,Fright hand.
