OL,6,F"At some point I would really like to
OL,7,Fmarry my partner", he said.
OL,9,F"But things like being able to raise a
OL,10,Ftoast at the reception - I couldn't
OL,11,Fhave done that before treatment
OL,12,Fwithout spilling my drink everywhere."
OL,14,F"Now, it shouldn't be a problem," he
OL,15,Fsays, with a big smile.
